@startuml
title AI Director Sequence — Core Flow
skinparam linetype ortho

actor Player
participant GameController
participant RoomFlowManager
participant AIDirector
participant EncounterManager
participant CombatResolver
participant RunLogger

== Start Run ==
Player -> GameController : Start New Run
GameController -> RoomFlowManager : initialize(seed)

note over GameController, RoomFlowManager
Dungeon generated (30 rooms)
Difficulty params loaded (read-only)
end note

loop For each room
  Player -> RoomFlowManager : Enter Room

  RoomFlowManager -> AIDirector : requestEncounter(room)
  AIDirector --> RoomFlowManager : EncounterPlan

  RoomFlowManager -> EncounterManager : applyPlan(plan)
  EncounterManager -> CombatResolver : beginCombat()

  Player -> CombatResolver : fight()
  CombatResolver --> RoomFlowManager : roomCleared()

  RoomFlowManager -> AIDirector : updateMetrics(roomResult)
  RoomFlowManager -> RunLogger : logRoom()
end

== End Run ==
alt Final Boss defeated
  RoomFlowManager -> RunLogger : logSummary(win)
  GameController -> Player : Victory
else Player HP <= 0
  RoomFlowManager -> RunLogger : logSummary(loss)
  GameController -> Player : Defeat
end

note over AIDirector
Deterministic:
decisions depend only on metrics + loaded params
end note

note over CombatResolver
Hard caps enforced (enemies/projectiles/waves)
end note

@enduml
